      <abstract id="aspace_d4e2f5e464fd1bb6c5fea3030316e6a4">Charles Morris Mount was an award-winning restaurant designer. Materials in the collection relate to Mount's work on numerous restaurant design projects and include menus, photographs, slides, transparencies, negatives, sketchbooks, design portfolios, newspaper clippings, correspondence, awards, audio recordings, and a computer disc. Materials date from 1980 to 2002.</abstract>
